Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.12,0:02:21.02,OP-Romanji,,0,0,0,,Ah... Koi ga...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.22,0:00:56.79,OP-CZ,,0,0,0,,Prosím, pojď se mnou, A~men,
